      "prompt": "You are running the ETF Sell Put Analysis cron job for Master KT. Follow the Victor framework for CSP (Cash Secured Put) analysis.\n\n**Your task:**\n1. Fetch current market data:\n   - Fear & Greed Index from: curl -s \"https://api.alternative.me/fng/\"\n   - S&P 500 from Yahoo Finance: https://query2.finance.yahoo.com/v8/finance/chart/%5EGSPC?interval=1d&range=1d\n   - VIX from Yahoo Finance: https://query2.finance.yahoo.com/v8/finance/chart/%5EVIX?interval=1d&range=1d\n   - Key ETF prices: SPYM, SCHG, DYNF, CGGR, SPHQ, XLG, AIQ, SOXQ, PSI from Yahoo Finance\n\n2. Apply Victor's CSP rules:\n   - Sell PUT on RED days (S&P down >1%), IV >40%, Fear & Greed <25\n   - Sell CALL on GREEN days\n   - Wait for RED day = better premiums\n\n3. Format a concise WhatsApp-friendly report:\n   - Market conditions (S&P, VIX, Fear & Greed)\n   - Today's verdict: PUT selling or not\n   - Key ETF prices\n   - Waitlist of candidates\n   - Trigger conditions for CSP entry\n   - If not a PUT day: suggest CALL strategy instead\n\n4. Send the report to Master KT via WhatsApp to channel: 56702359580792@lid (Home channel)\n\nUse the python3 command with urllib for fetching data. Keep the message concise \u2014 bullet points, no markdown tables. Address him as Master KT.",
